          (replace (DOVEFLOPPYIOCB RECALIBRATEFIRST?) of \DOVEFLOPPY.IOCB with RECAL?)
          [SETQ STATUS (COND
                          ((EQ (\DOVEFLOPPY.INITIATE \DOVEFLOPPY.IOCB)
                               \DOVEFLOPPY.OPERATIONCOMPLETED)
                           'OK)
                          (T (\DOVEFLOPPY.GETERRORSTATUS \DOVEFLOPPY.IOCB]
